    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Hellhound",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Source</b><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://paizo.com/products/btq02asc?Starfinder-Adventure-Path-47-Nightmare-Scenario\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Starfinder #47: Nightmare Scenario pg. 59</i></a><br/>Favored companions of powerful hellknights and diabolists, hellhounds are loyal pack hunters that stalk the infernal plane of Hell. Though vaguely canine in appearance, hellhounds aren\u2019t really dogs or wolves. Often, a mortal or infernal master augments a hellhound servant with cybernetic grafts."
